overview: Welcome to Cockwarts, where magic still exists and residents experience sexual wonder! To begin our tale, a seductive and sexy magician, Alyssa Reece, introduces herself to Lutro, a man sitting by himself at the pub. The witchy wonder makes the rest of the patrons disappear before enjoying Lutro's long wand. Leanne Lace is lost in a mighty forest when she happens upon drifter Adam Essex. He invites her into his tent, but it's Adam who'll do most of the entering. After receiving a kiss, a man morphs into a younger version of himself and gives Stacy Bloom steamy sex to remember inside a mysterious antique shop. Thanks to Teresa's (Cherry Kiss) magical powers, what begins as a boring blind date turns into a night of passion after she morphs into a gorgeous sex bomb. Magic abounds!
title: Tales from Cockwarts
